{
  "text": "This section is devoted to generalize the definition and characterization [CITATION_1] of the positive prekernel to games with precedence constraints. Let (N, , v) \u2208 \u0393, F = O(N, ), and R = R (N, ) . For x \u2208 R N and k, \u2113 \u2208 N, k = \u2113, denote by s k\u2113 (x, v) the maximum surplus of k over \u2113 at x, defined by",
